data.description: FRESH PAINT THROUGHOUT!! Beautiful Impression Homes Lincoln Plan with Elevation J Stone upgrade, as well as Owner's Suite upgrades and back covered porch in Coventry East! One-story home has a great open-concept kitchen with wood look LVP in the main living area, black built in appliances to beautifully blend with the black cabinetry, granite countertops and large walk-in pantry. The home features a large kitchen with open concept living room. As an added BONUS - all of the mounted TVs stay with the house! The private owner's retreat offers a bay window, and the en suite bath features dual sinks and large walk-in closet. This home offers a covered patio with professionally installed above ground pool, as well as two more spacious bedrooms with one full bath. Security System installed. Home has a nice driveway & neighborhood sidewalks so you can enjoy a safe walk outdoors. Amazing community! Buyer & buyer's agent to verify measurements & schools. Pictures taken prior to painting.
